'''Japan Street''' is a [[Special:MyLanguage/Worlds|world]] created by NEET ENGINEER.

The world exists on the PC and Quest platforms separately.

It was published in 2019 and has since grown to be one of the largest hubs for the Japanese [[VRChat]] Community.

