=PC & Quest worlds=
Due to the world size limitation of 50MB at the time, this world has been split between PC and Quest. 

The Quest world used to be updated regularly, but the updates have been suspended since the problem with VRChat for Quest crashing during world initialization. 

The current [https://vrchat.com/home/world/wrld_76b7fb21-1a84-4b49-bb04-f4510d03a358 Japan Street Quest] is based on PC's version 0.309 (excluding some functionalities).

=Concept=
'Japanese City that looks like it could exist in real life.' 

This world was developed through a collaboration of volunteers, with models being brought together to recreate a Japanese cityscape.

=Community=
There is an official VRChat group "[https://vrchat.com/home/group/grp_5192fe07-f10b-41b7-8a76-4773f7bbad5a Japan Street町内会]" which exists for this world.

